title: Ozric Tentacles - Album Collection (Part I)
description:
Hippie trippy music from the Ozrics:

- O Z R I C   T E N T A C L E S - 
   - Album Collection Part I -

Progressive rock or easy listening? Probably somehow inbetween.
By Gong and overtly Steve Hillage as their stylistic precursors
Ozric Tentacles are known for their spacy psychedelic jams and
ethnic (primarily middle eastern) implied soundscapes.

...all in all relaxing and pleasing music.


Part I:		1989 - Pungent Effulgent
		1990 - Erpland
		1991 - Strangeitude

Part II		1993 - Jurassic Shift
		1994 - Arborescence
		1995 - Become The Other

Part III:	1997 - Courious Corn
		1999 - Waterfall Cities
		2000 - The Hidden Step
		2000 - Swirly Termination

Part IV:	2004 - Spirals in Hyperspace
		2006 - The Floor's Too Far Away
		2009 - The Yumyum Tree

- This is the first torrent out of four that will be posted.

- All music files are compressed in lossless APE format (Monkey's Audio).
  Monkey's Audio Encoder is included (more efficient than FLAC but a bit
  slower).

Stay alert, the tentacles are already snatching at you!
